WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.583
Consider this predictive analysis scenario. You are implementing an autonomous

00:00:04.583 --> 00:00:09.167
Agentic AI workflow within a culturally diverse, globally distributed team.

00:00:09.167 --> 00:00:13.750
Predict the friction points using the SPLIT framework diagnostic tool.

00:00:13.750 --> 00:00:18.333
How will language differences and technological reliance amplify social distance?

00:00:18.333 --> 00:00:22.917
Propose a Stagility-based solution that balances the rapid AI deployment

00:00:22.917 --> 00:00:27.500
with empathic concern for the team's identity and processes. Finally,

00:00:27.500 --> 00:00:32.083
internally formulate a critique of your current leadership approach. Does

00:00:32.083 --> 00:00:36.667
your personal corporate leadership philosophy integrate self-awareness, conflict-agility, and empathy

00:00:36.667 --> 00:00:41.250
into a coherent causal system? The future belongs to leaders

00:00:41.250 --> 00:00:45.833
who can balance the cold calculus of technological scaling with

00:00:45.833 --> 00:00:50.417
the complex reality of human sustainability. Engineer the optimal climate

00:00:50.417 --> 00:00:55.000
for your teams, and lead with purpose.
